#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:156
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"You have arrived in Engi space. The Mantis have been threatening the Engi "
"core worlds, but you should be able to stock up for your journey."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:157
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You have arrived in Engi space. The fall of the Federation has brought tough"
" times for these robotic lifeforms, but they're usually willing to help."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:158
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You have arrived in Engi space. These masters of engineering will happily "
"help the Federation, however in the current situation, their trust must "
"first be earned."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:159
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"In this sector, there are many ships with advanced drone technologies. "
"Perhaps they can help you break away from the pursuing Rebel Fleet."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:160
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"You arrive in the once quite peaceful Engi sector. These mechanized "
"organisms can easily patch up your ship's hull. For a suitable fee, of "
"course."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:161
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"\"01010111 01100101 01101100 01100011 01101111 01101101 01100101 00100001\" "
"— These numbers inscripted on the entry beacon seem to be a greeting message"
" in binary! Oh those Engi..."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:162
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[7]"
msgstr ""
"The Engi have always been faithful allies of the Federation. They are ready "
"to help even now, when the chance of Federation victory is extremely slim..."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:163
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[8]"
msgstr ""
"You have arrived in a sector belonging to the Engi. This race is famous for "
"its adept engineering skills, so if you still haven't thought about "
"replenishing supplies or patching up your ship — now is the right time."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:164
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ENGI\"]/text[9]"
msgstr ""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:172
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ENGI\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"The Engi can do remarkable things with just a pile of scrap. The Engi hive "
"at this beacon are selling equipment for just that."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:173
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ENGI\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"A message arrives: \"Your scrap, ours. Our weapons for you.\" You're about "
"to raise the shields when you realize it's just an Engi trader looking for a"
" trade."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:174
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ENGI\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"An Engi ship hails: \"Engine upgrade necessary for travel home. Sale of "
"equipment necessary for engine upgrade.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:185
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"The complex arrangements of ship hulls and FTL drive capacitors floating "
"abandoned in space suggest the Engi were here not too long ago; but no "
"longer."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:186
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You arrive at a green planet with great plains and rolling waterfalls. It "
"would be of little interest to the Engi nearby."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:187
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You have arrived near an Engi construction yard. Most Engi maintain their "
"bi-pedal appearance out of habit but here you see a number of Engi hives "
"working together to create massive organic machines adept at building ships."
" Truly a sight to behold."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:188
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"Even though each \"individual\" Engi is made up of trillions of nano-"
"machines, their culture still revolves around traditional social "
"interactions. A nearby station seems to be constructed for entertainment of "
"passing Engi travellers."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:189
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"You see a number of Engi space stations and fleets nearby. Despite looking "
"like piles of junk loosely tied together they are actually a model of "
"efficiency. They just lack a certain aesthetic emphasis in their "
"constructions."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:190
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"This system appears quite peaceful. You're not sure how long it'll last "
"between the combined threats of the Rebels and Mantis."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:191
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[7]"
msgstr ""
"There are a number of merchant ships passing through the area despite the "
"threat of Mantis invasion. No doubt interested in buying the efficient "
"technology of the Engi."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:192
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[8]"
msgstr ""
"You see a small Rebel carrier in the distance. You lay low and try to blend "
"in with the other traffic. However it's surprising to see a Rebel military "
"ship alone deep in Engi space."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:193
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[9]"
msgstr ""
"The Engi seem to have avoided this particular node, along with every other "
"life-form. You keep your eyes peeled for reasons why, but spin up the FTL "
"without event."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:194
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ENGI\"]/text[10]"
msgstr ""
"A cluster of Engi satellites in orbit of a nearby planet are the only clue "
"the mechanical species was ever here. You have other places to be."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:214
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ENGI_GIFT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"An Engi vessel hails you. \"Identity: Federation? Outlier probability. "
"Implies... revival. Implies... hope. Assistance suggested.\" They offer some"
" supplies."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:215
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ENGI_GIFT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You cross paths with an Engi cargo vessel hurrying home before the Mantis "
"fleets attempt to take over this sector. They're happy to offload some of "
"their cargo to get home faster."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:216
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ENGI_GIFT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You make contact with an isolated Engi science station who are staying put "
"despite the likelihood of Mantis invasion. They suggest you trial some "
"experimental technology."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:217
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ENGI_GIFT\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"This was the site of a recent battle. Either a show of Mantis force, or the "
"Engi here weren't disposed to go peacefully. You pick through the pieces."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:221
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_FLEET_DELAY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You notice an Engi colony hiding on the other side of a nearby moon. It "
"turns out they're excavating an equipment cache from the Federation-Mantis "
"War, and they suggest it might be used to lure the pursuing rebel fleet."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:223
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_FLEET_DELAY\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Booby trap the cache."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:225
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_FLEET_DELAY\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You transfer down some missile warheads and the Engi rig them to blow before"
" setting a distress signal to attract the fleet's attention."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:233
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_FLEET_DELAY\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Secure the cache."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:235
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_FLEET_DELAY\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You have the Engi complete their excavations and bring the supplies on-"
"board."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:269
#, fuzzy
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_SURRENDER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"An Engi cruiser in the vicinity watches your arrival. Seeing you jump in "
"armed to the teeth, their captain immediately broadcasts its surrender: "
"\"Subject goal: wealth. Engi motivation: survival. Transfer of goods "
"acceptable?\""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:271
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_SURRENDER\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Explain that you're friendly."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:275
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_SURRENDER\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Accept their offer of surrender."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:277
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_SURRENDER\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engi obediently transfer over the goods and get on their way. Money for "
"nothing."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:284
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ENGI_SURRENDER_LIST\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engi seem relieved, and eager to get underway. They set off without "
"saying goodbye."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:287
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ENGI_SURRENDER_LIST\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engi seem relieved, and eager to get underway. They set off without "
"saying goodbye."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:290
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ENGI_SURRENDER_LIST\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engi are satisfied with your explanation. \"Beneficial. Subject goal: "
"long, long journey. Remains compatible with transfer of goods from Engi.\" "
"They send over the gear willingly, and you feel better for it."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:294
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ENGI_SURRENDER_LIST\"]/event[4]/text"
msgstr ""
"Learning that you are fighting on the side of the Federation, the Engi help "
"you improve your ship's reactor, as well as install an additional "
"augmentation."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:299
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ENGI_SURRENDER_LIST\"]/event[5]/text"
msgstr ""
"Learning that you are fighting on the side of the Federation, the Engi help "
"you improve your ship's reactor, as well as install an additional "
"augmentation."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:304
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ENGI_SURRENDER_LIST\"]/event[6]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engi calm down and Send your hull repair drone to your ship, which "
"patches up your ship."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:324
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ENGI_MANTIS_FIGHT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"A mixed radar signal turns out to be a Mantis attack ship scavenging the "
"remains of an Engi carrier. They turn and fight."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:325
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ENGI_MANTIS_FIGHT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You come across a Mantis raider taking pot shots at a defenceless Engi "
"supply station. Discovering its weapons aren't much of a match for the "
"station's armour, it turns on your ship. Battle stations!"

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:326
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ENGI_MANTIS_FIGHT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"The area looks clear, and you prepare to jump off, but a Mantis scout jumps "
"in behind you! They're as surprised as you are, but their weapons are "
"already online."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:327
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ENGI_MANTIS_FIGHT\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"You find a Mantis ship harrying a small squad of Engi. They make it to the "
"node and jump off, leaving you toe to toe with their pursuer!"

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:331
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_REBEL_FIGHT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The rebel fighter here would seem to suggest elements of the rebel fleet are"
" already making incursions on Engi space. You move to engage."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:336
msgid "data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_PIRATE_FIGHT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"There must have been rich pickings for pirates around here up until war "
"broke out. The pirate you encounter here looks worn down, but hungry. You'll"
" have to fight!"

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:349
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_STATION_DISTRESS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You receive a distress call from a nearby Engi ship: \"Assistance requested."
" Danger present. Imminent destruction.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:351
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_STATION_DISTRESS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Respond to the call and move in to assist."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:355
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ENGI_STATION_DISTRESS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Keep your distance."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:361
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ENGI_STATION_DISTRESS_LIST\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"You receive another message from the ship, this time with a Mantis at the "
"comm-log. \"Foolish meatsacks,\" he yells. Sensors indicate the ship is "
"moving in to attack and boarders teleport from the station."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:367
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ENGI_STATION_DISTRESS_LIST\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"You approach to find a Mantis ship assaulting a small Engi space station. "
"You prepare for a fight!"

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:374
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"SAVE_ENGI_STATION\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engi station is stripped bare and there are signs of a fierce battle. "
"The Mantis must have left the distress call active to lure other ships into "
"a trap."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:377
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"SAVE_ENGI_STATION\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"The station was in the process of being evacuated. A number of civilian Engi"
" express their gratitude as they finalize their preparations to leave. They "
"offer some fuel as a reward."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:381
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"SAVE_ENGI_STATION\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"The station hails you, \"Gratitude. Expected probability of defeat without "
"assistance... 86.2 percent. Request suitable reward.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:383
