"of Engi controlling this sector have come to the conclusion that other "
"races' ships can be useful to them."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:3341
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_MORPH\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The Morphs have deactivated modules that define the optimal ship "
"architecture to be the Engi design. They can thereby repair their damaged "
"ships with the wreckage of other ships — without scrapping them completely."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:3342
