"from organic materials originating from the Orchid homeworlds. Learning that"
" you represent the Federation, the Orchids agree to sell some military goods"
" as well."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8610
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ORCHID\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
