#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8612
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ORCHID\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You arrive at a beacon located near a planet in process of terraforming to "
"support plant life. There are no ships around. You prepare to jump away."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8613
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ORCHID\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"This beacon is devoid of any activity at the moment. The star is too dim, "
"providing insufficient energy for light dependent flora."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8623
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIND_DRONE\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Given how fragile Orchids are, they often resort to using drones to deal "
"with emergencies on their ships. A drone factory, still loyal to Federation,"
" is located at the beacon. Orchid engineers offer one of their creations for"
" free."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8624
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIND_DRONE\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"An Orchid freighter is waiting at the beacon. As soon as you jump in, they "
"message you: \"Too much cargo. Can't move. Please take some.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8625
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIND_DRONE\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"While the FTL drive charges, you decide to explore the surface of a planet "
"nearby. A depowered drone is hidden within the foliage of a giant tree, "
"probably left by pirates. You can find some use for it in your journey."

