#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIND_WEAPON\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"You are surprised to find a secret Federation station deep within Orchid "
"space. Its crew went as far as using traditional Orchid materials like "
"leaves and bark to hide the base. Allies at the station offer a weapon to "
"help on your journey."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8633
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIND_WEAPON\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"An Orchid colony at the nearby moon agrees to give you a weapon in exchange "
"for some rare plant specimen from your home planet you were lucky to have on"
" hand."

#: src-ru/data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber:8634
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_engi.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ORCHID_FIND_WEAPON\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"As you complete the jump, an Orchid ship explodes nearby for unknown "
"reasons. The only things that survive the explosion are some melted metal "
"parts and a single weapon."

